High volatility games pay out less often on average but the chance to hit big wins in a short time span is higher.
BLOCK WINS WITH RANDOM MULTIPLIER UP TO 256 X
Hit 3 or more SCATTER symbols to trigger additional free spins, as follows:
SCATTER symbol appears on all reels.
Only the highest win is paid per winning combination.
All symbols pay in blocks of minimum 5 symbols connected horizontally or vertically.

In the base game every symbol that is involved in a winning block has a random chance to carry a 2x multiplier. The total win of that block is multiplied by the product of all multipliers that are part of the combination with a maximum of 256x.
All wins are added to the player's balance after all of the tumbles resulted from a base spin have been played.
When winning with multiple blocks all wins are added to the total win.

In free spins every symbol that is involved in a winning block has a random chance to carry a 2x or 4x multiplier. The total win of that block is multiplied by the product of all multipliers that are part of the combination with a maximum of 256x. The chance to hit symbol multipliers is higher during the FREE SPINS ROUND.
The round starts with 10 free spins.
Tumbling will continue until no more winning combinations appear as a result of a tumble.
The maximum win amount is limited to {0}x bet. If the total win of a FREE SPINS ROUND reaches {1}x the round immediately ends, win is awarded and all remaining free spins are forfeited
The FREE SPINS ROUND with 10 starting free spins can be instantly triggered from the base game by buying it for 100x current total bet.

The TUMBLE FEATURE means that after every spin, winning combinations are paid and all winning symbols disappear. The remaining symbols fall to the bottom of the screen and the empty positions are replaced with new symbols coming from above.
Hit 3 or more SCATTER symbols to trigger the FREE SPINS FEATURE.
Special reels are in play during the feature.

The maximum win amount is limited to {0}x bet in both base game and free spin. If the total win of a FREE SPINS ROUND reaches {1}x bet the round immediately ends, win is awarded and all remaining free spins are forfeited
Malfunction voids all pays and plays.
The theoretical RTP of this game is {0}%

The TUMBLE FEATURE means that after every spin, winning combinations are paid and all winning symbols disappear. The remaining symbols fall to the bottom of the screen and the empty positions are replaced with symbols coming from above.
Tumbling will continue until no more winning combinations appear as a result of a tumble. There's no limit to the number of possible tumbles.

During the FREE SPINS round, whenever a MULTIPLIER symbol hits and the spin results in a win, the MULTIPLIER value gets added to the total multiplier. For the whole duration of the round, whenever any new MULTIPLIER symbol hits and results in a win the total multiplier value is also used to multiply the win.
The round starts with 15 free spins.
High volatility games pay out less often on average but the chance to hit big wins in a short time span is higher.
SCATTER symbol is present on all reels.
Whenever 3 or more SCATTER symbols hit during the FREE SPINS ROUND, 5 additional free spins are awarded.
These are the multiplier symbols. They are present on all reels and can hit randomly during spins and tumbles in both base game and FREE SPINS.
When winning with multiple symbols, all wins are added to the total win.
The FREE SPINS FEATURE is awarded when 4 or more SCATTER symbols hit anywhere on the screen.
The RTP of the game when using the "ANTE BET" is {0}%
The player has the option to select the bet multiplier. Depending on the selected bet, the game behaves differently. The possible values are:
Bet multiplier 20x - gives the ability to purchase a FREE SPINS ROUND by paying a value equal to 100x total bet.
All wins are added to the player's balance after all of the tumbles resulted from a base spin have been played.
Whenever a MULTIPLIER symbol hits, it takes a random multiplier value from 2x to 500x.

Symbols pay anywhere.
All wins are multiplied by base bet.
Special reels are in play during the FREE SPINS ROUND.
SPACE and ENTER buttons on the keyboard can be used to start and stop the spin.
Bet multiplier 25x - the chance to win free spins naturally is doubled. More SCATTER symbols are present on the reels. The FREE SPINS PURCHASE FEATURE is disabled.
When the tumbling sequence ends, the values of all MULTIPLIER symbols on the screen are added together and the total win of the sequence is multiplied by the final value.
Free spins total win in the history contains the whole win of the cycle.
Free spins win is awarded to the player after the round completes.
The RTP of the game when using "BUY FREE SPINS" is {0}%
Symbols pay anywhere on the screen. The total number of the same symbol on the screen at the end of a spin determines the value of the win.
The FREE SPINS ROUND can be instantly triggered from the base game by buying it for 100x current total bet. When the 25x ante bet feature is enabled, the BUY FREE SPINS feature is disabled.
All values are expressed as actual wins in coins.

serializableData._text: Pretoenia zdarma a bonusov vhry s pripotan k vhre platobjen lnii.
Po dokonen kola je hrovi udelen vhra pretoen zdarma.
Vetky vhry s nsoben zkladnou stvkou.
Vetky hodnoty s vyjadren ako skuton vhry v minciach.
Porucha zru vetky platby a hry.
Celkov vhra pretoen zdarma, v histrii hry, obsahuje celkov vhru cyklu.
Tlaidl SPACE a ENTER na klvesnici mu by pouit na spustenie a zastavenie pretoenia.
Hry s vysokou nestlosou vyplcaj v priemere menej asto, ale anca dosiahnu vek vhry v krtkom asovom rozpt je vyia
BLOKOV VHRY S NHODNM NSOBITEOM A 256 X

Zasiahnite 3 alebo viac symbolov SCATTER, aby ste spustili dodaton toenia zdarma
nsledovne:
Symbol SCATTER sa objavuje na vetkch valcoch.
Za vhern kombinciu je vyplaten je len najvyia vhra.

Vetky symboly vyplcaj v blokoch s minimlne 5 
symbolmi spojenmi horizontlne alebo vertiklne.

V zkladnej hre m kad symbol, ktor je zahrnut vo vhernom bloku, nhodn ancu nies 2x nsobitea.
Celkov vhra danho bloku sa vynsob sinom
vetkch nsobiteov, ktor s sasou kombincie s maximom 256x.

Vetky vhry sa pridaj k hrovmu zostatku po tom, o boli v hre vetky padnutia, ktor boli vsledkom 
zkladnho toenia.
Pri vhre s viacermi blokmi s vetky vhry pripotan v celkovej vhre.

Pri toeniach zdarma m kad symbol, ktor sa podiea na vhernom bloku, nhodn ancu nies nsobite 2x
alebo 4x. Celkov vhra toho bloku sa vynsob sinom vetkch nsobiteov, ktor s sasou kombincie s
maximom 256x. Poas KOLA S TOENIAMI ZDARMA je anca zasiahn nsobitele symbolov vyia.

Padnutie bude pokraova a km sa neobjavia iadne
alie vhern kombincie v dsledku padnutia.

Maximlna vhern suma je obmedzen na 5 000x stvku. Ak celkov vhra KOLA TOEN ZDARMA
dosiahne 5 000x, kolo sa okamite skon, vhra sa udel a vetky zostvajce toenia zdarma prepadn

KOLO TOEN ZDARMA s 10 tartovacmi toeniami zdarma me by
spusten okamite v zkladnej hre zakpenm za 100x aktulnnu
celkov stvku.
Symbol SCATTER vyhrva na ktorejkovek pozcii.

FUNKCIA PADNUTIA znamen, e pokadom toen s vyplaten vhern kombincie a vetky vhern
symboly zmizn. Zostvajce symboly padn na spodn as obrazovky a przdne pozcie sa nahradia
novmi symbolmi prichdzajcimi zhora.
Zasiahnite 3 alebo viac symbolov SCATTER, aby ste spustili FUNKCIU TOEN ZDARMA.
Poas funkcie s v hre pecilne valce.

Maximlna vhern suma je obmedzen na {0}x stvky v zkladnej hre a toeniach zdarma. Ak celkov vhra KOLA TOEN ZDARMA dosiahne {1}x stvky, kolo sa okamte ukon, vhra sa udel a vetky zostvajce toenia zdarma prepadn
Porucha zru vetky platby a hry.
Symbol SCATTER plat na akejkovek pozcii.
FUNKCIA PADNUT znamen, e po kadom pretoen s vyplaten vhern kombincie a vetky symboly zmizn. Zostvajce symboly spadn na spodn as obrazovky a przdne miesta sa nahradia padajcimi symbolmi.
Funkcia padnut bude pokraova, km sa nezobrazia iadne vazn kombincie v dsledku funkcie padnut. Funkcia padnut je neobmedzen.

Poas kola TOEN ZADARMO, kedykovek bude zasiahnut symbol NSOBITE a nsledkom toenia bude vhra, prid sa hodnota NSOBITEA k celkovmu nsobiteovi. Poas celho trvania kola, kedykovek bude zasiahnut akkovek nov symbol NSOBITEA a povedie k vhre pouije sa k nsobeniu vhry celkov hodnota nsobitea.
Hry s vysokou nestlosou vyplcaj v priemere menej asto, ale anca dosiahnu vek vhry v krtkom asovom rozpt je vyia.
Symbol SCATTER sa zabrazuje na vetkch valcoch.
Kedykovek je 3 alebo viac symbolov SCATTER zasiahnutch poas KOLA TOEN ZADARMO, bude vm udelench 5 dodatonch toen zadarmo.
Toto s symboly nsobitea. S prtomn na vetkch valcoch a mu zasiahnu nhodne poas toeni a padnut a padan v zkladnej hre a poas TOEN PADNUT.
Pri vhre s viacermi symbolmi sa vetky vhry pridaj k celkovej vhre.
FUNKCIA TOEN ZADARMO je udelen, ke bud 4 alebo viac symbolov SCATTER zasiahnut kdekovek na obrazovke.
RTP hry pri pouit "ANTE STVKY" je {0}%
Hr m monos vberu nsobitea stvky. V zvislosti od zvolenej stvky sa hra sprva inak. Mon hodnoty s:
Nsobite stvky 20x - dva monos zakpi KOLO TOEN ZDARMA zaplatenm hodnoty rovnajcej sa 100x celkovej stvky.
Vetky vhry s pridan k bilancii hra po tom, o boli hre vetky ukonen padnuta, ktor boli vyvolan zkladnm pretoenm.
Vdy, ke padne symbol MULTIPLIER, zska nhodn hodnotu nsobitea 2x, 3x, 4x, 5x, 6x, 8x, 10x, 12x, 15x, 20x, 25x, 50x, 100x, 250x alebo 500x.
Symboly platia kdekovek. Vetky vhry s nsoben zkladnou stvkou.
Poas KOLA PRETOEN ZADARMO s v hre pecilne valce.
Tlaidl SPACE a ENTER na klvesnici mu by pouit na spustenie a zastavenie toenia.
Nsobite stvky 25x - anca na vhru toen zdarma sa prirodzene zdvojnsob. Na valcoch je prtomnch viac symbolov SCATTER. FUNKCIA KPY TOEN ZDARMA nie je umonen.
Ke skon sekvencia padania, hodnoty vetkch symbolov NSOBITE na obrazovke sa staj a celkov vhra sekvencie sa vynsob konenou hodnotou.
Celkov vhra toen zadarmo, v histrii hry, obsahuje celkov vhru cyklu.
Po dokonen kola je hrovi udelen vhra toen zadarmo.
RTP hry pri pouit "KPI TOENIA ZDARMA" je {0}%
Symboly platia kdekovek na obrazovke. Celkov poet rovnakho symbolu na obrazovke na konci toenia uruje hodnotu vhry.
KOLO TOEN ZADARMO je mon okamite spusti v zkladnej hre zakpenm za 100x celkovej stvky. Ke je povolen ante stvka 25x, je funkcia NKUP TOEN ZADARMO deaktivovan.
Vetky hodnoty s vyjadren ako skuton vhry v minciach.
, ABY STE ZNSOBILI VHRY Z PADAN
ZVYUJCI SA NSOBITE PRI TOENIACH ZADARMO
Nsobite stvky 20x - dva monos zakpi KOLO TOEN ZDARMA zaplatenm hodnoty rovnajcej sa 100x celkovej stvky.
Nsobite stvky 25x - anca na vhru toen zdarma sa prirodzene zdvojnsob. Na valcoch je prtomnch viac symbolov SCATTER. FUNKCIA KPY TOEN ZADARMO nie je umonen.
Hr m monos zvi nsobitea stvok o 25% na 25x stvky na lniu. Pri hran aktvnou stvkou ante sa zvyuj ance na zasiahnutie symbolov Scatter.
Nsobite stvky 20x - dva monos zakpi KOLO TOEN ZADARMO zaplatenm hodnoty rovnajcej sa 100x celkovej stvky.
